author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
They're finally here! Teased way back in 2020 as the BIG NEW THING along with Kislev for The Old World, Cathay has been on the backburner for the first year of the game, but is FINALLY out for Pre Order now. Let's check it out!

Thanks to Games Workshop for the complimentary book to review.
